<H3> <TI>   'Arafat Considering Visit to Jericho on 5 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat Considering Visit to Jericho on 5 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0205090294 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 2 May 94 p 9 </F>
<F P=103> TA0205090294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Roni Shaqed and Orli Azulay-Katz] </F>
  [Excerpt] Yasir 'Arafat is considering the possibility of 
making a two-day visit to Jericho on 5 May, the day after the 
signing of the agreement between the PLO and Israel. This was 
discussed yesterday in talks between PLO and Israeli 
representatives. 
  'Arafat said he wants to visit to drum up support for the 
PLO 
and weaken Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] and those opposed 
to the agreement. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

