<H3> <TI>   Secretary Warren Christoper Arrives in Damascus </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Secretary Warren Christoper Arrives in Damascus </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Meets With President al-Asad </H4>

<F P=102> JN3004160394 Damascus SANA in Arabic 1550 GMT 30 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN3004160394 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus SANA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damascus, 30 Apr (SANA) -- At 1800 today, President 
Hafiz al-Asad received U.S. Secretary of State Warren 
Christopher. The meeting was attended by Faruq al-Shar', foreign 
minister, Dennis Ross, U.S. coordinator for Middle East peace 
Process, and Christopher Ross, U.S. ambassador in Damascus. 

</TEXT>

