<F P=102> NC0105082094 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian GMT 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0105082094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
