  [Text] Today in the Friday prayers sermons in Tehran 
Ayatollah Ahmad Jannati stressed that fighting against slackness 
and strengthening working ethics during the period of 
reconstruction should be given top priority. 
  Referring to the Workers' Week, the acting Friday imam of 
Tehran said: During the period of reconstruction the role of 
