<H3> <TI>   Armed Men Set Fire To Four Buses in Algiers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Armed Men Set Fire To Four Buses in Algiers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0305083694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 2 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0305083694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Regarding recent terrorist acts, four buses were set 
on fire this morning at 0400 by an armed group in the center of 
the capital. The operation took place on the road linking 
Bouzareah and Bab El Oued when the armed men forced the drivers 
out and set the buses on fire. This act cost the Urban 
Transport Company in the capital the loss of about 1 billion 
centimes. 

</TEXT>

