<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister, Iraqi Ambassador Note `Brotherly Ties' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister, Iraqi Ambassador Note `Brotherly Ties' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2804195694 Baghdad INA in Arabic 1950 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN2804195694 </F>
<F P=104>  Baghdad INA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Doha, 28 Apr (INA) -- Qatar's Foreign Minister 
Shaykh Hamad Bin-Jasim Bin-Jabr Al Thani today received Iraq's 
Ambassador to Qatar Anwar Sabri. 
  The meeting, attended by Shaykh Mish'al Bin-Hamad 
Bin-Khalifah Al Thani, addressed brotherly ties and regional 
developments. 

</TEXT>

