<H3> <TI>   Citizens Support Policy To Restore Golan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Citizens Support Policy To Restore Golan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0205135894 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1115 GMT 2 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0205135894 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Occupied Golan -- Syrian Arab citizens have declared 
their support for Syria's efforts to restore occupied Syrian 
Golan and to realize a full Israeli withdrawal from it. 
  In a statement issued yesterday and distributed in several 
cities and villages, the Syrian Arab citizens in the occupied 
Golan also expressed support for Syria's policy and principled 
stands toward the restoration of all of the Golan to Syria. 

</TEXT>

