<F P=100> ARABIAN PENINSULA </F>
<F P=101> Yemen </F>
<H3> <TI>   Artillery Brigade Reportedly Surrounded in Yarim </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Artillery Brigade Reportedly Surrounded in Yarim </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA0305211794 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1900 GMT 3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA0305211794 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A responsible source in the Defense Ministry has 
stated the following: A dangerous development in the miltiary 
incidents being directed by the ruling family in Sanaa has 
occurred. A number of Republican Guard, Central Security Force, 
tank, and armored vehicle units have taken up positions around 
the 1st Artilley Brigade in Yarim. The brigade's position 
became dangerous around 1200 today, when crowds [as heard] 
successively bore down on them. The Defense Ministry has briefed 
local, Arab, and international public opinion on the acts being 
carried out by the military command in Sanaa, and it places full 
responsibility on these rulers, whose appetite has been whetted 
by in-fighting among the sons of the homeland, the waste of 
their blood, and the resulting grave consequences. These events 
place the country on the brink of a devastating civil war that 
will destroy everything. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

