<H3> <TI>   UK Media Accused of Concealing Facts Over Lockerbie </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    UK Media Accused of Concealing Facts Over Lockerbie </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0305211094 Tripoli Libyan Television Network in Arabic 
1930 GMT 3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0305211094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli Libyan Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The UK newspaper THE INDEPENDENT has reported that 
the relatives of the victims of the Lockerbie accident are 
divided over a documentary film about this accident. This has 
prompted British official circles to intervene to prevent its 
showing, under the pretext that it would influence the course of 
the investigation into the affair. Although the Great 
Jamahiriyah has nothing to do with this film, the British media 
are endeavoring to conceal facts from the British people and 
they pick out what serves Britain's colonial purposes without 
respecting the truth and without showing any desire to let the 
British masses know all the facts. This is the method used by 
the western states to black out the facts of this affair. 

</TEXT>

